      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so it's more about the protons and the nerve signals than the acid itself. that makes sense. i've heard people talk about \"acidosis\" or something like that though... is that what happens when the buildup gets really bad? like does it actually damage the muscle tissue or just make it feel like it's burning?",
